    "en": {
      "title": "Record defense budget from Biden passed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The US House of Representatives has passed a record defense bill proposed by President Joe Biden, paving the way for the US defense budget to exceed $800 billion next year.",
        "The House voted 329 to 101 to pass its version of the National Defense Authorization Act, or NDAA, which sets policy for the Pentagon.",
        "The Senate has yet to pass its version, but the Senate Armed Services Committee has already proposed an increase over Biden's proposal."
      ],
